vote.title: An ordinance granting a revocable license to Sneaker Politics, LLC, for the use of approximately 9 square feet of aerial space to install, occupy and maintain an illuminated blade sign with premise over a portion of Main Street right-of-way near its intersection with Malcolm X Boulevard - Revenue: General Fund $1,000.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
